<Base title="Speaker" description="Speakers for effective e-commerce appearances – Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">Strategy</p>
<h1>Speaker for Effective E-Commerce Appearances</h1>
<p>Speakers are the link between online marketing and the classic advertising format of trade fairs and exhibitions. With our deep knowledge of your online shop and years of experience with success strategies for e-commerce, we present your business model successfully on site. Our know-how is also valuable for impulse workshops, seminars and lectures for students of the IT sector and online marketing.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>Book a Speaker for Your Company Presentation at Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Direct contact with the target audience remains the most direct form of advertising even in the age of digital commerce. We offer you our service in planning events as well as as speakers before your target audience. The focus of the address differs depending on whether it is internal for your IT managers or external for trade fair visitors, students and promotional audiences. When booking our speakers, you benefit from short lead times, as important basic knowledge about your business model and detailed knowledge about advertising-relevant products or services is already available.</p>
<h2>Occasions for Using Our Speakers</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Company events:</strong> A product launch, business expansion or the start of your new online shop brings the entire workforce including your project teams together in a less technical way for once. Our speakers provide strategic motivation for the next milestones of your business success in e-commerce.</li>
<li><strong>Workshops:</strong> Impulse workshops are particularly valuable for your IT department managers. They explain technological facts, set impulses for brainstorming and motivate team members to work together with a clear objective.</li>
<li><strong>University lectures:</strong> Students of the IT sector and online marketing initially know only theoretical prerequisites and fundamentals. Our lecturers can create practice-oriented lectures from a theoretical basis.</li>
<li><strong>Seminars:</strong> Further training in the digital age hardly leaves any employee untouched. Our speakers turn your competent employees into specialists for automations, advertising strategies, target group orientation and performance optimisation in e-commerce.</li>
<li><strong>Trade fairs:</strong> Nothing is as clearly target-group-oriented as a trade fair. With experience in your business model and appealing rhetoric from our speakers, you enthuse specialist audiences as well as visitors to a consumer goods fair for end consumers.</li>
<li><strong>Promotional events:</strong> Even on a small exhibition area, you present your products and services cleverly. Our speakers are crowd magnets and are happy to act as advisers for you already during promotional planning.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Convincing Your Industry of Your Competence with a Professional Speaker</h2>
<p>Enthusiasm is sparked by competence. Our speakers convey competence through vivid descriptions and inviting communication. Specialist audiences from the fashion industry, real estate and hotel sectors, food or automotive can ask targeted questions about a product or range area.</p>
<h2>Inspiring Target Groups with Speakers from Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>Just as diverse as the occasions at which speakers appear are the target groups. B2B specialist audiences are interested in online shops with goods for other businesses in their own B2C target group. Manufacturers are best presented on the D2C market because the speakers can convey insider knowledge directly from the development department to the target audience.</p>
<p><em>Would you like your products presented competently and inspiringly by a professional speaker? Contact Hob by Horse by telephone or <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">email</a> for seminars, lectures or workshops!</em></p>
</div></div>
</Base>
